<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢ -<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص١٨٠:</span> قَوْلُهُ تَعَالَى: {قُلْ هُوَ اللَّهُ أَحَدٌ <span class="c2">(١)</span> اللَّهُ الصَّمَدُ <span class="c2">(٢)</span>} <span class="c4">[الإخلاص: ١، ٢]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">يُقَالُ:</span> لاَ يُنَوَّنُ <span class="c3">{أَحَدٌ}</span>: أَيْ وَاحِدٌ "<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c3">{اللَّهُ الصَّمَدُ}</span>: <span class="c2">«العَرَبُ تُسَمِّي أَشْرَافَهَا: الصَّمَدَ»</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ أَبُو وَائِلٍ:</span> <span class="c2">«هُوَ السَّيِّدُ الَّذِي انْتَهَى سُودَدُهُ»</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>